Package: rmcop
Title: R Monte Carlo Option Pricing
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("WVTW5", "WVTW5", , "not_displayed@ucl.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package that contains functions for pricing financial options. rmcop supports Monte Carlo option pricing on several types of European options, including *vanilla option*, *Asian option*, **barrier option*, *binary option*, and *lookback option*. It also supports pricing via Black-Scholes formula and Binomial tree method for vanilla European and American options.
